THE LUCKY TOUR STARTS TONIGHT & U BEST BELIEVE WE’RE CELEBRATING 🥹🍀💘🥳 3 new songs are coming this friday on all streaming platforms & the lucky vinyl is now available for pre-order!

the vinyl will include the original 13 tracks plus the 3 new ones- fix you too ft. kameron marlowe, nothin’ crazy ft. mackenzie carpenter & reasons to stay. i wanted to include these extra songs as a thank you for embracing my debut album and loving it as much as you have over these past few months - y’all have completely made this the best year yet already 😭 i appreciate y’all more than you know & can’t wait to see y’all on the road soon!🍀💚🍀💚🍀💚🍀

Y’all really changed my life this past year & when I get asked what my favorite part of all of this craziness has been, my answer is always The Lucky Tour. In every city, you showed up early, you made homemade tshirts & signs & bracelets, & you sang (screamed) every word to every song - just fulllyyyyy showed up. We laughed & cried together & I’ve never felt closer to y’all. #grouptherapy ‼️

26 shows across the country & we wrapped it up in Georgia last night. I’m overwhelmed with gratitude & won’t ever take this life y’all let me live for granted. I’ve got the best fans, best team & best band out there - thank you for loving my debut album the same way I do 💘🫶🏼🍀 🎰 Gonna go cry now bye!

📸: @cece_dawson
